### ===============================
### 基础配置（按需修改）
### ===============================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ===============================
### 1. 查询全部告警
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 2. 查询未处理告警
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts?status=UNRESOLVED
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 3. 查询已处理告警
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts?status=RESOLVED
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 4. 查询告警日志（默认分页）
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/logs
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 5. 按状态筛选日志（未处理）
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/logs?status=UNRESOLVED
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 6. 按告警类型筛选（倾斜告警）
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/logs?alert_type=TILT_ABNORMAL
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 7. 按时间范围筛选
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/logs?start_time=2026-04-01T00:00:00&end_time=2026-04-16T23:59:59
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 8. 分页查询
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/logs?page=1&page_size=10
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 9. 多条件组合查询
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/logs?status=UNRESOLVED&alert_type=TILT_ABNORMAL&page=1&page_size=5
Accept: application/json



### ===============================
### 11. 错误测试：非法状态
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts?status=XXX
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### 12. 错误测试：时间格式错误
### ===============================
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/logs?start_time=abc
Accept: application/json